mogudu ( english : husband ) is a 2011 telugu drama film produced by nallamalapu srinivas ( bujji ) on lakshmi narasimha productions banner , directed by krishna vamsi . starring gopichand , taapsee pannu in the lead roles with rajendra prasad , roja and naresh in supporting roles . music composed by babu shankar as his first debut . the film recorded as flop at box office . the film is all about how a man truly becomes husband when he understands his wife and wins her love . the film released on 4 november 2011 . later film dubbed in hindi as mard ki zaban . it was dubbed into tamil as my dear purushan .